Description.value: This iFlow enables SAP SuccessFactors to initialize assessments on ADP Tax Credit systems. The iFlow receives the new assessment request from SAP SuccessFactors, collects extra information about the candidate and sends the candidate data to ADP APIs. In response, ADP will generate a unique assessment test URL which SAP SuccessFactors can provide to candidates.

name.value: ADP Tax Credits SuccessFactors Connector Order Assessment

query.value: SELECT applicationId FROM AssessmentOrder WHERE id = '${property.AssessmentOrderId}'
